data.description: This beautiful and spacious mobile home sits on 0.25 acres of land in Waycross only minutes from Ware High School, Coastal Pines and South Georgia State College. There are plenty of great memories to be made in this 4 bedroom 3 bath home. This property features a large living room with 2 additional flex spaces on opposite ends of the home. The primary bedroom has it's own nice size walk in closet. The bathroom in the owner's suite includes a garden tub and walk in shower shown in pictures. The 3 bedrooms all have nice size walk in closets.
